RawLine: TNPC_60076737,大福叔你是在{color=#FF0000}未時{/color}鑄劍，而劍鋒派與飛白派弟子，委託鑄劍時辰都是{color=#FF0000}午時{/color}。從劍鋒派的語氣聽來如此肯定，我想一定是他先的了。,大福叔你是在{color=#FF0000}未时{/color}铸剑，而剑锋派与飞白派弟子，委托铸剑时辰都是{color=#FF0000}午时{/color}。从剑锋派的语气听来如此肯定，我想一定是他先的了。

Items.mt: Uncle Dafu, you are casting the sword at the hour of midnight, while the disciples of the Jianfeng Sect and the Fei Bai Sect, commissioned to cast the sword at the hour of noon. From the tone of the Jianfeng Sect sounded so sure, I think it must be his first.
